# A simple program to calculate the area of a rectangle.

say "--- Rectangle Area Calculator ---"

set length to ask "Enter the length:"
set width to ask "Enter the width:"

# A more advanced version would have math operators.
# For v1.0, we'll just show the inputs.
say "You entered a length of", length, "and a width of", width
say "Mewar v2.0 will be able to calculate the area!"


#####OutPut#######
--- Rectangle Area Calculator ---
Enter the length: **10**
Enter the width: **5**
You entered a length of 10 and a width of 5
Mewar v2.0 will be able to calculate the area!
